and tell 'em anything you want.

36:10.834 --> 36:14.125
Your father's going down
either way.

36:14.125 --> 36:16.291
- What do you have?
- All of it.

36:16.291 --> 36:19.375
The body, weapon,
Cochran.

36:26.291 --> 36:29.458
Who do you think
is more powerful in this town,

36:29.458 --> 36:31.834
you or Andrew Finney?

36:35.917 --> 36:37.458
I don't know.

36:37.458 --> 36:40.875
Why don't you go up there
and find out?

36:40.875 --> 36:43.667
Or tell the truth
and get it all.

36:43.667 --> 36:45.250
Who knows?
You play your cards right,

36:45.250 --> 36:46.375
you might even keep the team.

36:50.792 --> 36:54.208
You think
that's all I care about.

36:54.208 --> 36:57.709
♪ dramatic music ♪

36:57.709 --> 36:59.208
He hit him
with a fireplace poker.

36:59.208 --> 37:02.500
I saw the whole thing.

37:02.500 --> 37:06.291
You're saying
you were there for this?

37:06.291 --> 37:09.458
I walked in,
saw them both covered in blood.

37:09.458 --> 37:14.333
♪♪♪

37:16.583 --> 37:20.834
[screaming]

37:20.834 --> 37:23.208
Ms. Finney...

37:23.208 --> 37:26.500
...why would your father
kill your husband?

37:26.500 --> 37:31.333
♪♪♪

37:39.250 --> 37:42.208
They were lovers.

37:42.208 --> 37:44.250
Unsubstantiated accusations
like that--

37:44.250 --> 37:46.083
It's the truth.

37:46.083 --> 37:50.166
♪♪♪

37:50.166 --> 37:51.208
Are you protecting
Ray Donovan?

37:51.208 --> 37:53.041
Why would I do that?

37:53.041 --> 37:54.250
Because you're afraid
for your life.

37:54.250 --> 37:55.250
We know he's threatened
your family.

37:55.250 --> 37:57.250
Who told you that, my dad?

37:57.250 --> 37:58.667
We won't let him hurt you.
You're safe here.

37:58.667 --> 38:01.625
Ray didn't do it.
My dad did.

38:01.625 --> 38:03.750
- Ms. Finney--
- What if I told you

38:03.750 --> 38:05.542
where the body was,
an exact location?

38:05.542 --> 38:09.041
You'd be legally obligated
to investigate it, right?

38:09.041 --> 38:11.792
Of course.

38:11.792 --> 38:14.542
♪♪♪

38:14.542 --> 38:16.333
- [coughs]
- Get me out of here! Come on!

38:16.333 --> 38:18.750
Ray! Ray!
Come on!

38:18.750 --> 38:22.083
Get me out of here, man.
Come on, man.

38:22.083 --> 38:25.709
♪♪♪

38:25.709 --> 38:28.083
Dad.

38:28.083 --> 38:31.959
Paige. Darling.
What is it?

38:31.959 --> 38:35.917
I just wanted to stop by
on my way home.

38:35.917 --> 38:37.917
- I just gave my statement.
- Oh, thank you.

38:37.917 --> 38:39.041
Y-you--

38:39.041 --> 38:41.166
We did the right thing.

38:41.166 --> 38:43.333
♪♪♪

38:43.333 --> 38:45.166
It'll all be over soon.

38:45.166 --> 38:47.250
Well, the trial
will be a terrible distraction,

38:47.250 --> 38:49.208
but we'll come through it
stronger than ever,

38:49.208 --> 38:52.542
and I do want to apologize
to you for what I said before.

38:52.542 --> 38:53.750
You were right.

38:53.750 --> 38:55.542
I did bring him
into the family.

38:55.542 --> 38:56.875
That's on me.

38:56.875 --> 39:01.959
♪♪♪

39:06.125 --> 39:10.500
Let me out of here, Ray.
Ray! Ray!

39:10.500 --> 39:15.333
♪♪♪

39:15.333 --> 39:17.583
I'll take good care
of the business, you know.

39:17.583 --> 39:20.125
Of course you will,
when the time comes.

39:20.125 --> 39:21.083
[chuckles]

39:21.083 --> 39:24.625
Never doubted that.

39:24.625 --> 39:28.125
You've been a great mentor.

39:28.125 --> 39:30.125
Well, I've made mistakes.

39:30.125 --> 39:31.917
Everybody does.

39:31.917 --> 39:33.417
Part of the territory.

39:33.417 --> 39:35.583
But I mean on balance.

39:35.583 --> 39:39.250
No, look where you are.

39:41.667 --> 39:44.125
And look what you've done.

39:44.125 --> 39:46.709
♪♪♪

39:46.709 --> 39:49.291
You're being sentimental.

39:49.291 --> 39:52.041
♪♪♪

39:52.041 --> 39:53.750
Good-bye, Dad.

39:53.750 --> 39:58.583
♪♪♪

