40:40.667 --> 40:42.875
You sure you want those
to be your last words?

40:42.875 --> 40:46.375
Fuck you, Ray.

40:46.375 --> 40:48.500
All right, wait, wait.

40:48.500 --> 40:50.375
Don't worry, Cochran.

40:50.375 --> 40:54.750
You got the rest of your life
to look forward to.

40:54.750 --> 40:57.417
[tires squealing]

41:21.917 --> 41:24.750
[sighs]

41:42.417 --> 41:45.291
You think you're pretty
fucking smart, don't you?

41:45.291 --> 41:47.166
Not as smart as I used to be.

41:47.166 --> 41:48.583
I got a brain disease.

41:48.583 --> 41:51.291
You're gonna get
in that fucking truck,

41:51.291 --> 41:52.208
and you're gonna leave.

41:52.208 --> 41:53.083
You hear me?

41:53.083 --> 41:54.959
Or I'm taking you in.

41:54.959 --> 41:56.291
Oh, yeah?
Where?

41:56.291 --> 41:57.500
Sunny Creek Medical Center.

41:57.500 --> 42:00.792
Trust me,
it's a real shithole.

42:00.792 --> 42:03.291
I'm afraid
I don't like, uh, either

42:03.291 --> 42:06.417
