42:06.417 --> 42:07.667
Fuck you.
Let's go.

42:23.500 --> 42:26.291
They don't want me to go, Ray.
You know why?

42:26.291 --> 42:28.875
Because I make them feel good.

42:28.875 --> 42:30.333
You don't make
people feel good.

42:30.333 --> 42:32.834
You make them feel small
and shitty.

42:38.041 --> 42:41.333
What are you gonna say
to the family, Ray, huh?

42:41.333 --> 42:44.333
Either you tricked
their beloved grandfather

42:44.333 --> 42:45.667
into signing away his rights,

42:45.667 --> 42:47.250
or you're the kind of son

42:47.250 --> 42:49.625
