in a nursing home.

42:49.625 --> 42:52.375
Either way,
they're gonna hate you.

42:58.333 --> 43:00.875
Checkmate, Ralph.

43:00.875 --> 43:03.125
Ralph, no.
Randy?

43:03.125 --> 43:05.166
I'm sorry.
I forgot your name.

